VFIを実行する¶

  • 10001
In [9]:
count = 1

# maxit
for it = 1:params.maxit

    vkp = zeros(params.nk, params.nk)

    # 4.
    for i = 1:params.nk
        vkp[:, i] = util[:, i] + params.*vfcn
    end

    # 5.
    for i = 1:params.nk
        Tvfcn[i] = maximum(vkp[:, i])
        Tpfcn[i] = argmax(vkp[:, i])
    end

    # 6.
    dif1 = maximum(abs.((Tvfcn-vfcn)./vfcn))
    dif2 = maximum(abs.(Tpfcn-pfcn))

    # 
    vfcn = deepcopy(Tvfcn)
    pfcn = deepcopy(Tpfcn)

    # 
    # ()
    dif[1, it] = dif1
    dif[2, it] = dif2

    # ()
    if it==1 || it==3 || it==5
        val_tmp[:, count] = vfcn
        count = count + 1
    end

    # println("iteration counter: $it")
    # println("error (value): $dif1")
    # println("error (policy): $dif2")
    # println()

    # 
    if dif1 < params.tol
        val_tmp[:, end] = vfcn
        break
    end

    if it == params.maxit
        println("The model does not converge")
    end
end

In [14]:
"""
(discretized DP).

### Arguments
`params::Params`: 

### Returns
`vfcn::Vector{Float64}`: 
`pfcn::Vector{Float64}`: 
`cfcn::Vector{Float64}`: 
`dif::Vector{Float64}`: 
`val_tmp::Vector{Float64}`: 
"""
function ddp(params::Params)

    count = 1 # 

    # 
    vfcn = zeros(params.nk)
    pfcn = zeros(Int64,params.nk)
    Tvfcn = zeros(params.nk)
    Tpfcn = zeros(Int64,params.nk)

    val_tmp = zeros(params.nk, 4) # 
    dif = zeros(2, params.maxit); # 

    # 
    #  (0)
    util = -10000.0*ones(params.nk, params.nk)

    # 
    wealth = params.kgrid.^params. + (1-params.)*params.kgrid

    # (k,k')
    for i = 1:params.nk, j = 1:params.nk
        cons = wealth[i] - params.kgrid[j]
        if cons > 0.0
            util[j, i] = MyEconFcn.crra(cons, params.)
        end
    end

    # VFI
    for it = 1:params.maxit

        vkp = zeros(params.nk, params.nk)

        for i = 1:params.nk
            vkp[:, i] = util[:, i] + params.*vfcn
        end

        for i = 1:params.nk
            Tvfcn[i] = maximum(vkp[:, i])
            Tpfcn[i] = argmax(vkp[:, i])
        end

        # 
        dif1 = maximum(abs.((Tvfcn-vfcn)./vfcn))
        dif2 = maximum(abs.(Tpfcn-pfcn))

        # 
        vfcn = deepcopy(Tvfcn)
        pfcn = deepcopy(Tpfcn)

        # 
        #()
        dif[1, it] = dif1
        dif[2, it] = dif2

        # ()
        if it==1 || it==3 || it==5
            val_tmp[:, count] = vfcn
            count = count + 1
        end

        println("iteration counter: $it")
        println("error (value): $dif1")
        println("error (policy): $dif2")
        println()

        if dif1 < params.tol
            val_tmp[:, end] = vfcn
            break
        end

        if it == params.maxit
            println("The model does not converge")
        end
    end

    return vfcn, pfcn, dif, val_tmp

end

⬆で計算した政策関数は最大値の位置なので、政策関数の値に変換¶

In [16]:
policy = zeros(params.nk)
for i = 1:params.nk
    policy[i] = params.kgrid[pfcn[i]]
end
In [17]:
# 
util = zeros(params.nk)
valfn = zeros(params.nk)

for i = 1:params.nk
    cons = params.kgrid[i]^params. + (1-params.)*params.kgrid[i] - policy[i]
    util[i] = MyEconFcn.crra(cons, params.)
    valfn[i] = util[i] / (1-params.)
end
In [18]:
# 
AA = (1-params.)^(-1) * (log(1-params.*params.) + ((params.*params.)/(1-params.*params.))*log(params.*params.))
BB = params. / (1 - params.*params.)
v_true = AA .+ BB*log.(params.kgrid)
p_true = params.*params.*(params.kgrid.^params.);
